        "### Few-shot Prompt Design\n",
        "\n",
        "A Few-shot prompt provides the model with several examples (typically 3-5) of the task, which helps the model understand the patterns and nuances required for accurate classification. This approach is often more effective than Zero-shot or One-shot for complex tasks or when specific output formatting is crucial."
